{
  "stem": "4686.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] But it-- it-- it wasn't that long that we really missed, as-- as I say again, it's-- it's the children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What-- what-- how much did the adults had or not, it was the most important thing was that the children shouldn't miss.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We've been in the ghetto for 12 days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not know exactly where they are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they wanted money, and they wanted watches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody cared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have money, and we didn't have watches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then a couple of-- half an hour or so later, the Russian military police arrived with their bright green hats.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were able to let us know what's happening, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by the morning, they started to bring us the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was frightening still because there were still fighting going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Budapest was in-- in ruins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no electricity.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't know where to and what to and who is what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went-- It was cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was snow.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went to see what happened with our homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The house, our house, where we lived was very badly damaged.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We find very little there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We knew that we can't move in there because the roof wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no window.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The big house door was broken down and et cetera.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Grandparents lived too much out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we decided that we rather move in-- try to move into my Auntie [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Bergie ?] place, who lived in [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Baroschutso ?] on the fourth floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's turned out that naturally some refugees were living in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was a three-room reasonably modern apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
